message.body: Oh good! Hitting up the OJ, nice hahah. I'm good, trying to get some stuff done in the next few hours. I've been up since 8 something and The day kind of flew by so far.
That's good! Normal time to get up, lol.
We should get lunch soon! Feels like I haven't talked to you in awhile. And we need to eat burgers :)
Yes! It's been a while... And burgers ehh? lol. Urge?
Yes! Those beef patties are calling out to me hahah!!! And so is it's friends, the bacon strips and avocado slices :)
